title: How to make fast money and nanites
author: Sphynxcolt

items.content:
Fly into space. You will find many asteroids. Mine them with your photon cannon or the phase beam.
You can get: Tritium, gold, silver or platinum and sometimes gold nuggets.
Keep the tritium as fuel for your pulse engine.
You can sell the gold, silver and platinum at a galactic trade terminal. You can find them in space stations.

On some planets you can find larval cores, albumen pearls or living pearls.
You can find the larval cores on the overworld and sometimes in caves. Attention: be very alerted because as soon as you try to pick it up, strange creatures are trying to kill you.
In caves you can find orb plants. You can open them and take teir albumen pearl. You can oly stack 5 of them.
On planets with water you will stumble across armored clams. When you swim near them they will open themselves and show theyir pearl. Pick it up but dont waste your time! Ass soon as you got the pearl they will close And hurt you.
You can sell the pearls and orbs at a trade terminal or refine the larval orb to nanites
